The word musical versatility means the ability of the musical artist of exploring the different genres, trying to produce distinct sounds
The musical versatility is distinguished into two different aspects.
One is the versatility of the Music Composer, Music Director and Music Producer of creating and producing sounds of different genres, inventing new sounds, fusing sound of different genres into one piece of musical work often called as fusion music.
Another is the versatility of vocalist, the versatility of the vocalists, is classified upon their talent and ability to sing songs of the different genres, hit high notes and lower notes effectively. And having a broad vocal range.
